    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- 末世下的“昭和美国”与“死而复生的少女” -</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/8e9e5338cf5904ce6defb2e42e62f885.poster.avif?t=1762941417\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/8e9e5338cf5904ce6defb2e42e62f885.webm?t=1762941417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/8e9e5338cf5904ce6defb2e42e62f885.mp4?t=1762941417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >昭和66年，日本凭借强大的经济实力，买下了大半个美国；随着移民潮将日本文化不断带入，两种不同的文化在这里激烈碰撞与融合，一幅未曾设想的“昭和美国”图景就此出现。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/23d6691e1bc902865e96ecf2028d5ffd.poster.avif?t=1762941417\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/23d6691e1bc902865e96ecf2028d5ffd.webm?t=1762941417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/23d6691e1bc902865e96ecf2028d5ffd.mp4?t=1762941417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，一场不明的“灾变”突然袭来，整个社会体系迅速瓦解；不知过了多久，一名“死而复生的少女”突然从土里爬出，展现在她眼前的，只有成群的丧尸、可怕的怪物、以及在末世中抱持不同信念的残存人类。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一切究竟是怎么回事？为了解开心中的疑团，少女踏上了将彻底改变她的末世冒险之旅。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- 兼具“爽快感”与“策略性”的战斗 -</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 少女被赋予的除了第二次的生命，还有可怕的谜之力量。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/18ca9140a9b33f3e859f701d6e5613ff.poster.avif?t=1762941417\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/18ca9140a9b33f3e859f701d6e5613ff.webm?t=1762941417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/18ca9140a9b33f3e859f701d6e5613ff.mp4?t=1762941417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作强调凶狠直接的战斗方式。玩家将在快节奏的高速战斗中，面对成群来袭的敌人，灵活地进行移动、攻击、闪避等。准备好用番茄酱洗个澡吗? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/8be5ffb83081abfb9b42dd2efaf9af21.poster.avif?t=1762941417\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/8be5ffb83081abfb9b42dd2efaf9af21.webm?t=1762941417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/8be5ffb83081abfb9b42dd2efaf9af21.mp4?t=1762941417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >近战武器、远程武器、还有其他怪怪的武器，应有尽有。玩家能够自由选择和搭配性能各异的武器，使用不同的战斗动作和攻击方式，与特征鲜明的敌人展开对抗。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- 在“充满时代感的旅途”中“生活与成长” -</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 末世旅途中，不仅仅是战斗。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/94b5a541289901570b8e4a4499880275.poster.avif?t=1762941417\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/94b5a541289901570b8e4a4499880275.webm?t=1762941417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/94b5a541289901570b8e4a4499880275.mp4?t=1762941417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作将带领玩家回到充满回忆的80年代，在横跨美国的旅途中，探索形形色色的角色和故事，感受“昭和美国”独特的风土人情。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/5dda039717f81b1cbba92abb46006f36.poster.avif?t=1762941417\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/5dda039717f81b1cbba92abb46006f36.webm?t=1762941417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687540/extras/5dda039717f81b1cbba92abb46006f36.mp4?t=1762941417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以巨大的房车为家，运用在旅途中探索和战斗获得的武器、服装、物品、道具以及经验等，玩家能够通过各种有趣的生活行为来提升不同方面的能力；当然，还包括那些充满时代记忆和意想不到的迷你游戏。在末世下积极地生活，不断成长吧。</p>",
